    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >项目：零假设是一个身临其境的恐怖游戏，你重温爱丽丝韦伯的生命的最后时刻，一个研究员在李尔公司谁消失在密室。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/52dc52488cce52ffeafd6970919d8aa0.avif?t=1772401487\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演爱丽丝发现的录音，与他一起探索异常空间。 当你漫步在一望无际的走廊和令人恐惧的熟悉的房间时，你会发现密室的阴险秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/e8b01bbf19c7a2a941527cc680a7332c.avif?t=1772401487\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他的笔记是解决问题的关键。 让自己沉浸在他的噩梦中，重温他在密室中的最后一天，并发现严峻的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/d5ce67c411a2412dc3ccfc14a6cfb66b.avif?t=1772401487\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能理解爱丽丝在遭遇未知命运之前发生了什么吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/83cc0ee7fb3c01ccc6f1e009b8752c3d.poster.avif?t=1772401487\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/83cc0ee7fb3c01ccc6f1e009b8752c3d.webm?t=1772401487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181720/extras/83cc0ee7fb3c01ccc6f1e009b8752c3d.mp4?t=1772401487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自KinTstudio，Lear公司团队的祝你好运</p>",
